                <quote>A man saw a ball of gold in the sky; </quote>
                <quote>He climbed for it, </quote>
                <quote>And eventually he achieved itâ€” </quote>
                <quote>It was clay. </quote>
                <quote/>
                <quote>Now this is the strange part: </quote>
                <quote>When the man went to the earth </quote>
                <quote>And looked again,</quote>
                <quote> Lo, there was the ball of gold. </quote>
                <quote>Now this is the strange part: </quote>
                <quote>It was a ball of gold. </quote>
                <quote>Aye, by the heavens, it was a ball of gold.</quote>
